text: Karyna Kazlouskaya is an archer from Belarus. Kazlouskaya competed at the 2020 Summer Olympics.Karyna KAZLOUSKAYA She was born on 18 July 2000.Karyna Kazlouskaya == References == Category:Living people Category:2000 births Category:Belarusian archers Category:Olympians for Belarus
